episodes.title: I Joined a Cult for 6 Days (It changed my life)
episodes.description:
Do you have a call to adventure for me and my camera? 
Email me at yousef.abughazaleh@gmail.com or DM me on instagram https://www.instagram.com/thepalestiniankuwaiti/?hl=en

This is the story of Damanhur, the world's only self-labelled 'ethical cult'.

Discover Damanhur:
https://damanhur.org
https://damanhur.travel
https://www.instagram.com/damanhur_spiritual_community/
